00:34:18,806 --> 00:34:20,475
Prêtes? Allez.

481
00:34:21,476 --> 00:34:22,977
You missed. One point for Yu-rim.

482
00:34:24,812 --> 00:34:25,646
Allez.

483
00:34:28,107 --> 00:34:29,150
Back to your positions.

484
00:34:34,072 --> 00:34:36,991
NA HEE-DO, KO YU-RIM

