00:34:38,701 --> 00:34:40,161
Prêtes? Allez.

486
00:34:40,244 --> 00:34:43,706
NA HEE-DO, KO YU-RIM

487
00:34:45,041 --> 00:34:46,417
One point for Hee-do.

